"hentry","category-wisdom-al-hikmah","tag-charity-al-sadaqah","tag-death-mawt","tag-good-character-husn-khuluq","tag-hereafter-akhirah","tag-manners-adab","tag-punishment-al-uqubah","tag-responsibility-al-masuliyyah","tag-reward-al-ajr","tag-whims-al-hawa","tag-worldly-life-dunya","tag-worship-al-ibadah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-149","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":12295,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/18\/suicide-funeral-prayer-janazah\/","url_meta":{"origin":4101,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Suicide: Praying over a Muslim who kills himself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Samurah reported: A man killed himself and the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, did not pray over him. Al-Tirmidhi said, \u201cThe people of knowledge disagreed on this issue. Some of them said that the Muslims should perform funeral prayers over every person who prayed towards Mecca,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19246,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/28\/long-life-many-hasanat\/","url_meta":{"origin":4101,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Life: Best people have long lives, many good deeds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 28, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakrah reported: A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, who are the best people?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cOne whose life is long and his deeds are good.\u201d The man said, \u201cWho are the worst people?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cOne whose life is long\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31987,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/12\/angels-guide-unwilling-judge\/","url_meta":{"origin":4101,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Authority: Allah sends angels to guide an unwilling judge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever seeks to be a judge and asks others to intercede so he can have it, he will be left to himself. Whoever is forced into it, Allah will send down an angel to direct him.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43004,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/10\/prefer-white-garments\/","url_meta":{"origin":4101,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Clothes: Prefer white garments, living or deceased","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 10, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cClothe yourselves in white garments, for they are the best of garments, and shroud your deceased in them.\u201d Ibn al-Mubarak, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cThe most beloved to me is to shroud oneself\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32727,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/09\/martyrs-protected-pain-death\/","url_meta":{"origin":4101,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Shahid: Martyrs protected from pain of death","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe martyr does not feel the pain of being killed except as one of you feels the pinch of an insect bite.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1668 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14271,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/18\/qadr-amal-bil-khawatim\/","url_meta":{"origin":4101,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Khawatim: Deeds are recompensed by their endings","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Sahl ibn Sa\u2019d reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, a man may appear to people as doing the deeds of the people of Paradise, yet he is among the people of Hellfire. Verily, a man may appear to people as doing the deeds\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhaditho